Class TeamsPlayersView

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class TeamsPlayersView
extends MyPanel
    This class implements the graphic view to show during the team's configuration's view.

    This class contains all the graphic elements needed to show the team's configuration and the information resulting from it. This class extends from MyPanel which is a generic, standard view. This class contains a set of JLabel, JTextField, JComboBox and JButton to let the user choose between the multiple configuration options for the teams and show him feedback information.

    Version:
    v0.1 03/18/2014
    Author:
